{"tid":480954,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想學結他","createTime":"2017-11-26T16:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T18:06:54.000Z","uid":155715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e96d68b4d76a5622cf0748c7b3611cd823522a2c","tid":480954,"uid":155715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"一直都想學返樣樂器<br />\n所以揀左結他<br />\n之前係出面學個幾堂<br />\n不過好似乜都冇學過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近排又想學返結他<br />\n試過上網搵片自學<br />\n不過學極都唔識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想搵人教下<br />\n希望至少可以彈下流行曲咁<br />\n有冇咩介紹？"},{"pid":"5742ae627620387b7b390aebb49b6105e7c96102","tid":480954,"uid":15863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"beyond<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a55d9bcc3492763eb5e444dcfeba6846098236e","tid":480954,"uid":121705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"首先要練好F chord , 100 個人學結它，有50個人因爲𨍭唔倒F chord 而放棄，玩得叻唔叻都好，不要做放棄𠴱50個"},{"pid":"ee8508b5cba6dfc710746b3c6b275c1a12eb0382","tid":480954,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先要練好F chord , 100 個人學結它，有50個人因爲𨍭唔倒F chord 而放棄，玩得叻唔叻都好，不要做放棄𠴱50個</blockquote><br />\nf有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nc先難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66005a1d5156e8a822efdc0c870ac2ba5d2acb6","tid":480954,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:44:43.000Z","msg":"你而家識啲咩?　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caa5726c7042c578912f2efb82069620894006b","tid":480954,"uid":36165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"學結他真係最緊要practice,唔好怕手指痛<br />\n一過左最初手指既問題其實就可以輕鬆彈歌。<br />\n<br />\n如果淨係想彈到流行曲的話，自學最好，因為唔難，無謂比幾百蚊先學得個4堂。如果真係自學唔到就搵最平既，學到個竅門就ok。"},{"pid":"ee2122c126cc4a500b63d2689f81fa7a821cda0e","tid":480954,"uid":155715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你而家識啲咩?　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以話係零,乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cb30f535169c39c3451cf3da142fd32b449d9a","tid":480954,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"想搵個結他老師<br />\n有無將軍澳附近既？"},{"pid":"33092b0908430813095435d6f9b54c762f1b1c1b","tid":480954,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想搵個結他老師<br />\n有無將軍澳附近既？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675eb10c1296699cdb81997cc01ff564e253b191","tid":480954,"uid":45565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首先要練好F chord , 100 個人學結它，有50個人因爲𨍭唔倒F chord 而放棄，玩得叻唔叻都好，不要做放棄𠴱50個</blockquote><br />\nf有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nc先難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪講緊bar chord F<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98c3220f0ac574324c1acb87c4ae4322ff41731","tid":480954,"uid":137319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>首先要練好F chord , 100 個人學結它，有50個人因爲𨍭唔倒F chord 而放棄，玩得叻唔叻都好，不要做放棄𠴱50個</blockquote><br />\nf有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nc先難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪講緊bar chord F<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nF好似仲有第二個按法個一隻手指按哂兩條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋好多歌基本上係C A D G組成 學識呢幾個再比啲時間學學bar chord基本上都可以彈到一般流行曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1cf65799f95364dfe54f983d017b07a8e2e41","tid":480954,"uid":37078,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"Youtube:<br />\n[urlhttps://]<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/swy999[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fswy999%5B%2Furl%5D&d=6KY5%2B%2Bidm%2FivE4CZQQ%2F1mv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b20c5ae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.youtube.com/swy999[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\nfb page     <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/a a&rsquo;aa&iquest;&fnof;plays-music/430639887082691?ref=h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fa%C2%8D%20a%E2%80%99aa%C2%BF%C6%92plays-music%2F430639887082691%3Fref%3Dh&d=6KY5%2B%2Bidm%2FivE4CZQQ%2F1mv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ef7f2923\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pages/a a&rsquo;aa&iquest;&fnof;plays-music/430639887082691?ref=h</a> <br />\n<br />\nig: <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/jimmyshum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjimmyshum&d=6KY5%2B%2Bidm%2FivE4CZQQ%2F1mv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=715ad9df\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/jimmyshum</a> <br />\n <br />\n學結他:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1w3tAezaHFkqw3tv7neMWZxqWdf1HTZHAInBOJKDNgIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1w3tAezaHFkqw3tv7neMWZxqWdf1HTZHAInBOJKDNgIw&d=6KY5%2B%2Bidm%2FivE4CZQQ%2F1mv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e66a771d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1w3tAezaHFkqw3tv7neMWZxqWdf1HTZHAInBOJKDNgIw</a>"},{"pid":"c6da533c9a2af1b04a4eb64390e0dd63a47d20c4","tid":480954,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi